Package org.eclipse.egf.core.ui.workbench.action.explorer.create

Class Summary
AbstractCreatePatternLibraryAction Base class to implement actions that create a pattern library.
CreateContextAction Create a model element Context as a child of its parent.
CreateContextElementAction Open a wizard to create an ContextElement model element.
CreateContractElementAction Open a wizard to create an ContractElement model element.
CreateDomainAction Open a wizard to create an Domain path.
CreateFactoryComponentInvocationAction Open a wizard to create an FactoryComponentInvocation model element.
CreateMappingAction Open a wizard to create a MappingModel model element.
CreateModelElementAction Base class to implement an action to open a wizard that creates a NamedModelElementWithId object.
CreatePatternAction Open a wizard to create a PatternModel model element.
CreatePatternLibraryAction Open a wizard to create a PatternLibrary model element as a child of another pattern library.
CreateRootPatternLibraryAction Open a wizard to create a PatternLibrary model element as a 'root' pattern library.
CreateTaskFactoryHolderAction Open a wizard to create an TaskFactoryHolder model element.
